 coriander in mixing bowl then chop <b>3 sec\/speed 7<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula."},{"content":"Add miso paste, soy sauce and mirin then mix <b>5 sec\/speed 4<b>. Rub garlic-ginger marinade all over chicken and set Varoma aside."},{"isHeader":true,"content":"Broth"},{"content":"Place onion and chilli in mixing bowl then chop <b>3 sec\/speed 5<b>. Transfer to simmering basket and set aside."},{"content":"Place mushrooms, oil, stock paste and water in mixing bowl then insert simmering basket with onion and chilli. Place Varoma with chicken into position and steam <b>45 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>."},{"content":"Add eggs to Varoma dish, arranging them around the chicken, then cover Varoma with Varoma lid and steam <b>10-15 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>, or until chicken and eggs are cooked. Set Varoma aside and allow chicken and eggs to cool. Remove simmering basket with aid of spatula and discard contents."},{"content":"Re-insert simmering basket, then weigh udon noodles into it and cook <b>1 min 30 sec\/100°C\/speed 1<b>. Remove simmering basket with aid of spatula, drain noodles, then divide between 4 serving bowls."},{"content":"Re-insert simmering basket, then weigh in carrots, corn and tenderstem broccoli then cook <b>5-8 min\/100°C\/\/speed 1<b>. Remove simmering basket with aid of spatula, drain vegetables, then divide between the serving bowls placing over noodles. Season broth to taste with salt, then set aside to keep warm."},{"content":"Shred reserved cooled chicken meat with 2 forks and discard carcass. Divide shredded chicken evenly between the serving bowls."},{"content":"Peel reserved cooled eggs, cut each egg in half and add 2 halves to each serving bowl. Pour broth into serving bowls, then garnish with spring onions, coriander leaves, fried shallots and nori strips (if using). Serve immediately."}],"basicInfo":["medium","30m","1h 35m","4 portions"]}